<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.6">
<l>erinta paiṅka ṇilaṅkupēḻvā yeyiṟṟoṭi tevvuruveṉ</l>
<l>ṟirintu vāṉōr kalaṅkiyōṭa viruntavam māṉatiṭam</l>
<l>nerinta vēyiṉ muḻaiyuṇiṉṟu nīṇeṟi vāyuḻuvai</l>
<l>tirinta vāṉaic cuvaṭupārkkuñ ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the lord who sat [there] so that celestials scurried,</l>
<l rend="indent">bewildered, fleeing,</l>
<l>Saying, “What form is this with glowing green eyes [and] glittering teeth</l>
<l rend="indent">in a cavernous mouth?”</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain where a tiger, waiting in a lair of dense bamboo</l>
<l rend="indent">along a long path,</l>
<l>Peers out at the tracks of an elephant that has wandered [there].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
